        &lt;h2 id=&#34;data-sources&#34;&gt;Data Sources&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#data-sources&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
